{"tid":1716400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國外交部關注香港暴力升級","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:37:13.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f91268000a5c5c300a22e3683cb46119d8fa8f","tid":1716400,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"英國外交部發言人形容，當日發生的事件令人非常憂慮，嚴重關注持續的暴力和示威者與警方之間的升級。發言人指，<strong>示威者應該避免暴力，警方亦不能以不合比例的方式回應</strong>，各方需要透過對話尋找出路。<br />\n<br />\n警方當日於西灣河槍傷一名示威者，另外亦有一名男子於馬鞍山被點燃成火人，二人情況危殆。事件反映持續逾五個月的示威衝突再次升級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/397159/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F397159%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=f917ab8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/397159/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1</a>"},{"pid":"7f0ff2b0f4bbef2a5cb1e1016abb3f9021d7c21e","tid":1716400,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952eda669aa